00:17:18.490 --> 00:17:20.130 align:middle line:90%
So that's the memory component.

00:17:20.130 --> 00:17:24.319 align:middle line:84%
But literally, every
aspect of our anatomy

00:17:24.319 --> 00:17:27.573 align:middle line:84%
has conductive abilities,
storage abilities.

00:17:27.573 --> 00:17:28.740 align:middle line:10%
>>SUE: Everything is energy.

00:17:28.740 --> 00:17:31.440 align:middle line:84%
It's just moving and vibrating,
and it's all a communication

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:32.240 align:middle line:90%
system.

00:17:32.240 --> 00:17:34.665 align:middle line:84%
This whole system
is, and I'm thrilled

00:17:34.665 --> 00:17:37.350 align:middle line:84%
to hear that you're
working with this directly.

00:17:37.350 --> 00:17:41.700 align:middle line:84%
Body Memory Recall-- can you
tell us about what that is,

00:17:41.700 --> 00:17:43.045 align:middle line:90%
specifically?

00:17:43.045 --> 00:17:43.920 align:middle line:90%
>>TRIPODI: Well, yes.

00:17:43.920 --> 00:17:46.890 align:middle line:84%
It's a form of the
body work that really

00:17:46.890 --> 00:17:48.450 align:middle line:90%
incorporates many techniques.

00:17:48.450 --> 00:17:51.870 align:middle line:84%
