00:20:30.110 --> 00:20:31.820 align:middle line:84%
>>SUE: What do you
think the element is

00:20:31.820 --> 00:20:34.400 align:middle line:90%
that makes it so effective?

00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:36.950 align:middle line:84%
>>TRIPODI: The key
element is that A,

00:20:36.950 --> 00:20:40.460 align:middle line:84%
