00:20:43.100 --> 00:20:44.000 align:middle line:90%
are out there.

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:47.210 align:middle line:84%
If you ask all
those practitioners,

00:20:47.210 --> 00:20:49.610 align:middle line:84%
is your goal to help
release body memory?

00:20:49.610 --> 00:20:51.360 align:middle line:90%
They'd probably say no.

00:20:51.360 --> 00:20:52.670 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:20:52.670 --> 00:20:57.170 align:middle line:84%
So without the intent, most
of the time it doesn't happen.

00:20:57.170 --> 00:21:00.620 align:middle line:84%
So intention and
secondly, education.

00:21:00.620 --> 00:21:03.830 align:middle line:84%
If a person comes in
to receive body memory,

00:21:03.830 --> 00:21:06.420 align:middle line:90%
they've been educated about it.

00:21:06.420 --> 00:21:09.940 align:middle line:84%
And they've already prepared
themselves psychologically,

00:21:09.940 --> 00:21:10.740 align:middle line:90%
emotionally.

00:21:10.740 --> 00:21:12.980 align:middle line:84%
They're ready to
receive that healing.

00:21:12.980 --> 00:21:15.890 align:middle line:84%
So intention, education,
and the last thing is touch.

00:21:15.890 --> 00:21:18.420 align:middle line:84%
Your touch, the quality
of your touch-- again,

00:21:18.420 --> 00:21:21.110 align:middle line:84%
connecting with the
