00:21:34.190 --> 00:21:35.180 align:middle line:90%
a person in there.

00:21:35.180 --> 00:21:37.790 align:middle line:84%
And that feels like
a physical workout,

00:21:37.790 --> 00:21:39.860 align:middle line:90%
a physical manipulation.

00:21:39.860 --> 00:21:41.690 align:middle line:84%
And it can feel
very good, but it

00:21:41.690 --> 00:21:45.420 align:middle line:84%
doesn't help us to get access
to those protective responses.

00:21:45.420 --> 00:21:48.460 align:middle line:84%
So the key is to come
out of protection.

00:21:48.460 --> 00:21:50.360 align:middle line:84%
What's going to
help you to do that?

00:21:50.360 --> 00:21:53.180 align:middle line:84%
To me, nothing
better than touch,

00:21:53.180 --> 00:21:57.110 align:middle line:84%
a loving touch, a safe touch,
but one that actually connects

00:21:57.110 --> 00:22:00.110 align:middle line:84%
with you inside, because
where we're afraid

00:22:00.110 --> 00:22:01.910 align:middle line:90%
is where we feel alone.

00:22:01.910 --> 00:22:04.940 align:middle line:84%
So when somebody connects
with that part of you that's

00:22:04.940 --> 00:22:07.640 align:middle line:84%
alone and afraid
energetically, it

00:22:07.640 --> 00:22:10.290 align:middle line:84%
has magical effects
of transformation.

00:22:10.290 --> 00:22:12.290 align:middle line:84%
>>SUE: And this works for
people that don't even

