an emotional symptom,

00:22:55.830 --> 00:22:59.090 align:middle line:10%
a psychological symptom,
a stress of some kind.

00:22:59.090 --> 00:23:01.160 align:middle line:84%
They might have a
theoretical idea

00:23:01.160 --> 00:23:04.160 align:middle line:84%
