of things that maybe you

00:23:30.290 --> 00:23:31.830 align:middle line:90%
had forgotten about.

00:23:31.830 --> 00:23:35.450 align:middle line:84%
So all of that comes, and
it's a very natural process.

00:23:35.450 --> 00:23:37.680 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: What is unwinding?

00:23:37.680 --> 00:23:39.590 align:middle line:84%
>>TRIPODI: Unwinding
is a term that

00:23:39.590 --> 00:23:45.830 align:middle line:84%
describes the release step of
body memory transformation.

00:23:45.830 --> 00:23:48.680 align:middle line:84%
So what happens is the
body-- once the defenses

00:23:48.680 --> 00:23:51.390 align:middle line:84%
drop and the suppressed
energy moves through the body,

00:23:51.390 --> 00:23:52.790 align:middle line:90%
it moves the body.

00:23:52.790 --> 00:23:55.010 align:middle line:84%
So the body will
spontaneously move.

00:23:55.010 --> 00:23:55.970 align:middle line:90%
You're not moving it.

00:23:55.970 --> 00:23:56.780 align:middle line:90%
I'm not moving it.

00:23:56.780 --> 00:23:58.820 align:middle line:90%
It's just moving on its own.

00:23:58.820 --> 00:24:02.450 align:middle line:84%
As suppressed energy is
moving through the tissues,

00:24:02.450 --> 00:24:06.050 align:middle line:84%
moving through all your anatomy,
it's moving your anatomy.

00:24:06.050 --> 00:24:08.450 align:middle line:84%
So your body goes into
different positions.

00:24:08.450 --> 00:24:10.430 align:middle line:90%
It shakes.

00:24:10.430 --> 00:24:14.870 align:middle line:84%
Again, spontaneous emotions
come up and are expressed.

00:24:14.870 --> 00:24:18.860 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes people go into
positions of injury or trauma.

00:24:18.860 --> 00:24:20.780 align:middle line:84%
So that's called
positional memory.

00:24:20.780 --> 00:24:24.560 align:middle line:84%
But that whole dynamic
release response

00:24:24.560 --> 00:24:27.260 align:middle line:90%
is given a term unwinding.

00:24:27.260 --> 00:24:31.490 align:middle line:84%
It's like we get wound up, and
then when we heal, we unwind.

00:24:31.490 --> 00:24:32.480 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: Excellent.

00:24:32.480 --> 00:24:36.110 align:middle line:84%
