And that's where we feel hard
and tight and even painful

00:26:39.550 --> 00:26:40.360 align:middle line:90%
in our body.

00:26:40.360 --> 00:26:42.318 align:middle line:84%
>>SUE: Science is showing
us in energy medicine

00:26:42.318 --> 00:26:45.310 align:middle line:84%
