00:26:51.710 --> 00:26:52.510 align:middle line:90%
impulse.

00:26:52.510 --> 00:26:56.570 align:middle line:84%
So it's actually carrying
communication as well.

00:26:56.570 --> 00:26:58.030 align:middle line:84%
