00:30:32.320 --> 00:30:34.120 align:middle line:84%
And energies are
just moving out.

00:30:34.120 --> 00:30:37.100 align:middle line:84%
And the end result is you
feel like you've been birthed.

00:30:37.100 --> 00:30:37.900 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: Yeah.

00:30:37.900 --> 00:30:38.310 align:middle line:90%
Oh, here I am.

00:30:38.310 --> 00:30:40.520 align:middle line:84%
>>TRIPODI: You feel lighter
and fresh and alive again.

00:30:40.520 --> 00:30:41.295 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, here I am.

00:30:41.295 --> 00:30:43.545 align:middle line:84%
>>SUE: Now, once someone has
this experience with you,

00:30:43.545 --> 00:30:45.610 align:middle line:84%
can they continue to
do this on their own?

00:30:45.610 --> 00:30:47.980 align:middle line:84%
Once they recognize that,
oh, here's what I have to do,

00:30:47.980 --> 00:30:51.020 align:middle line:84%
I have to let go in this way
and allow this thing to happen,

00:30:51.020 --> 00:30:52.520 align:middle line:84%
they can continue
it on their own?

00:30:52.520 --> 00:30:53.937 align:middle line:84%
>>TRIPODI: That's
the takeaway, is

00:30:53.937 --> 00:30:55.840 align:middle line:84%
that when you
remember how to let

00:30:55.840 --> 00:30:59.170 align:middle line:84%
go, because it is a remembering,
once you remember how

00:30:59.170 --> 00:31:02.410 align:middle line:84%
to let go, that's the
positive body memory,

00:31:02.410 --> 00:31:04.420 align:middle line:90%
is you go, oh, yeah.

00:31:04.420 --> 00:31:06.640 align:middle line:90%
This actually feels good.

00:31:06.640 --> 00:31:07.940 align:middle line:90%
This is really OK.

00:31:07.940 --> 00:31:09.730 align:middle line:90%
I can trust this process.

00:31:09.730 --> 00:31:12.310 align:middle line:84%
Then when you're in
your everyday life

00:31:12.310 --> 00:31:14.710 align:middle line:84%
and you have stresses
into your life,

00:31:14.710 --> 00:31:18.250 align:middle line:84%
you can begin to become
aware of the habit

00:31:18.250 --> 00:31:21.820 align:middle line:84%
to survive and suppress
and just switch gears.

00:31:21.820 --> 00:31:24.520 align:middle line:90%
And you can self-unwind at home.

00:31:24.520 --> 00:31:27.190 align:middle line:84%
I usually tell people to
do it in a quiet place,

00:31:27.190 --> 00:31:30.190 align:middle line:84%
private place, on the
floor with pillows,

00:31:30.190 --> 00:31:33.790 align:middle line:84%
so that their body is free to
move and stretch and release

00:31:33.790 --> 00:31:34.960 align:middle line:90%
and make sounds.

00:31:34.960 --> 00:31:37.060 align:middle line:84%
Cry if you need to,
whatever needs to happen,

00:31:37.060 --> 00:31:39.700 align:middle line:84%
that you're uninhibited
in the process.

00:31:39.700 --> 00:31:40.540 align:middle line:90%
Light a candle.

00:31:40.540 --> 00:31:41.520 align:middle line:90%
Put some music on.

00:31:41.520 --> 00:31:42.320 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: Yeah.

00:31:42.320 --> 00:31:44.920 align:middle line:84%
What is it that
you would suggest

00:31:44.920 --> 00:31:47.080 align:middle line:84%
that someone do to
be able to cultivate

00:31:47.080 --> 00:31:50.200 align:middle line:90%
their own ability to unwind?

00:31:50.200 --> 00:31:52.315 align:middle line:84%
Are there ways
that they can live?

00:31:52.315 --> 00:31:53.440 align:middle line:90%
Are there lifestyle things?

00:31:53.440 --> 00:31:55.065 align:middle line:84%
Are there things they
can pay attention

00:31:55.065 --> 00:31:58.360 align:middle line:84%
to that are going to enhance
their ability to sense

00:31:58.360 --> 00:32:01.120 align:middle line:84%
and perceive, oh, this
needs to be happening,

00:32:01.120 --> 00:32:04.880 align:middle line:84%
and my body really wants
to just untangle or unwind

00:32:04.880 --> 00:32:05.680 align:middle line:90%
in this area?

00:32:05.680 --> 00:32:07.870 align:middle line:84%
Is there anything that
you can suggest for people

00:32:07.870 --> 00:32:10.580 align:middle line:84%
to begin to cultivate
their ability to do this?

00:32:10.580 --> 00:32:11.380 align:middle line:90%
>>TRIPODI: Yes.

00:32:11.380 --> 00:32:14.240 align:middle line:84%
I would say there's
a few things.

00:32:14.240 --> 00:32:16.990 align:middle line:84%
First, consider the
opposite of suppression.

00:32:16.990 --> 00:32:18.820 align:middle line:90%
The opposite is expression.

00:32:18.820 --> 00:32:22.210 align:middle line:84%
So just getting mindful
of all of your tendencies

00:32:22.210 --> 00:32:27.580 align:middle line:84%
throughout the day to suppress
movement, to suppress emotion,

00:32:27.580 --> 00:32:32.050 align:middle line:84%
to suppress sound, or suppress
communication or words,

00:32:32.050 --> 00:32:33.950 align:middle line:90%
and simply shift.

00:32:33.950 --> 00:32:35.430 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to express.

00:32:35.430 --> 00:32:37.630 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to let my
body move in this way.

00:32:37.630 --> 00:32:39.740 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to let some sound out.

00:32:39.740 --> 00:32:43.300 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to let myself feel
and express what I'm feeling,

00:32:43.300 --> 00:32:45.130 align:middle line:84%
maybe not in the
moment it's happening

00:32:45.130 --> 00:32:47.960 align:middle line:84%
if it feels inappropriate,
but in a private place.

00:32:47.960 --> 00:32:48.760 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: In some way.

00:32:48.760 --> 00:32:50.052 align:middle line:90%
>>TRIPODI: That's a good start.

00:32:50.052 --> 00:32:52.630 align:middle line:84%
The other is to begin
educating yourself more

00:32:52.630 --> 00:32:54.130 align:middle line:90%
about this phenomenon.

00:32:54.130 --> 00:32:57.190 align:middle line:84%
And I recommend my book,
Freedom from Body Memory,

00:32:57.190 --> 00:32:59.380 align:middle line:84%
only because it
lays the foundation,

00:32:59.380 --> 00:33:02.020 align:middle line:84%
and we need to
understand the experience

00:33:02.020 --> 00:33:07.220 align:middle line:84%
before we feel necessarily safe
in entering the experience.

00:33:07.220 --> 00:33:13.900 align:middle line:84%
Lastly, there's no substitute
for being in a class or retreat

00:33:13.900 --> 00:33:19.425 align:middle line:84%
environment or even having
the BMR body work directly.

00:33:19.425 --> 00:33:23.260 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't be where I'm
at today in this process

00:33:23.260 --> 00:33:24.860 align:middle line:90%
if I didn't have help.

00:33:24.860 --> 00:33:25.660 align:middle line:90%
We need help.

00:33:25.660 --> 00:33:27.130 align:middle line:84%
>>SUE: Get over the hump
when you get started.

00:33:27.130 --> 00:33:28.797 align:middle line:84%
>>TRIPODI: We need
to get over the hump.

00:33:28.797 --> 00:33:30.760 align:middle line:84%
So a three-day
retreat or a class

00:33:30.760 --> 00:33:34.870 align:middle line:84%
will help jump start you into
this experience that's totally

00:33:34.870 --> 00:33:37.540 align:middle line:90%
natural but ultimately foreign.

00:33:37.540 --> 00:33:39.040 align:middle line:90%
And we just need to remember.

00:33:39.040 --> 00:33:41.020 align:middle line:84%
And then we can
take off on our own.

00:33:41.020 --> 00:33:46.540 align:middle line:84%
There's also physical stretching
you can do with balls and foam

00:33:46.540 --> 00:33:50.530 align:middle line:84%
rollers and other forms
of yoga that can take you

00:33:50.530 --> 00:33:55.900 align:middle line:84%
into an unwinding state if you
have remembered how to unwind.

00:33:55.900 --> 00:33:59.380 align:middle line:84%
Everyday stretching can
turn into an unwinding

00:33:59.380 --> 00:34:01.250 align:middle line:84%
if you have cultivated
that ability.

00:34:01.250 --> 00:34:02.050 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: Right.

00:34:02.050 --> 00:34:05.080 align:middle line:84%
If you can recognize that
subtle threshold, where

00:34:05.080 --> 00:34:07.510 align:middle line:84%
it goes from being
intentional about something

00:34:07.510 --> 00:34:10.030 align:middle line:84%
