00:40:30.450 --> 00:40:32.670 align:middle line:84%
had recommended
that I go see him.

00:40:32.670 --> 00:40:36.360 align:middle line:84%
And so I showed up not
really knowing what BMR was

00:40:36.360 --> 00:40:39.060 align:middle line:90%
all about but ready to say yes.

00:40:39.060 --> 00:40:42.520 align:middle line:84%
I was diagnosed with
fibromyalgia when I was 19.

00:40:42.520 --> 00:40:45.430 align:middle line:84%
