00:40:59.850 --> 00:41:04.530 align:middle line:84%
It was completely
unbelievable to me.

00:41:04.530 --> 00:41:08.650 align:middle line:84%
So I started going about twice
a week for about three months.

00:41:08.650 --> 00:41:11.220 align:middle line:84%
And after that
time, I was healed.

00:41:11.220 --> 00:41:13.350 align:middle line:90%
I didn't have any more pain.

00:41:13.350 --> 00:41:16.515 align:middle line:84%
>>SUE: And what was your
experience inside of that?

00:41:16.515 --> 00:41:18.950 align:middle line:90%
This is just fantastic.

00:41:18.950 --> 00:41:22.060 align:middle line:90%
What happened along the way?

00:41:22.060 --> 00:41:25.890 align:middle line:84%
>>ANGIE: Well, I got
access to a lot of things

00:41:25.890 --> 00:41:27.450 align:middle line:84%
that I experienced
in my childhood

00:41:27.450 --> 00:41:32.250 align:middle line:84%
