those things that you block out

00:41:38.730 --> 00:41:41.070 align:middle line:84%
or those things that you might
be afraid of even feeling

00:41:41.070 --> 00:41:42.570 align:middle line:90%
or remembering.

00:41:42.570 --> 00:41:44.430 align:middle line:84%
Those things did come
up in my sessions,

00:41:44.430 --> 00:41:46.440 align:middle line:84%
but that was the source
of what was actually

00:41:46.440 --> 00:41:49.800 align:middle line:84%
