headlights, I am a little kid

00:41:55.650 --> 00:41:57.300 align:middle line:84%
and I have no
choice in the matter

00:41:57.300 --> 00:41:59.800 align:middle line:90%
and I have nowhere to go.

00:41:59.800 --> 00:42:02.712 align:middle line:84%
That started to really store
up and accumulate in my body.

00:42:02.712 --> 00:42:04.170 align:middle line:84%
So when I did those
sessions, I was

00:42:04.170 --> 00:42:08.730 align:middle line:84%
able to access those memories
and then feel them and release

00:42:08.730 --> 00:42:10.410 align:middle line:90%
them.

00:42:10.410 --> 00:42:13.950 align:middle line:84%
And then my body was free of
the pain and all of the things

00:42:13.950 --> 00:42:17.340 align:middle line:90%
